snippet.title: Super Bash Goats | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Download now at: https://somewhatbasicgames.itch.io/super-bash-goats
For more information, please visit: http://facebook.com/SuperBashGoats/

Super Bash Goats is a local multiplayer brawler where you and your friends bash it out to see who becomes King Goat of the Mountain!
